  "prompt": "Who is Teresa Fidlago, and what is she known for?",
  "response": "Teresa Fidlago is a fictional character from a popular urban legend and hoax that originated in Spain. The story claims that Teresa Fidlago was a young woman who died in a tragic car accident. According to the legend, her ghost appears in a video that was supposedly filmed by a group of friends driving at night. In the video, they pick up a hitchhiker who turns out to be Teresa, and eerie events unfold.\n\nThe hoax gained widespread attention after a video titled \"Aterrador Video De La Joven Teresa Fidalgo\" (Terrifying Video of the Young Teresa Fidalgo) went viral on social media platforms. The video was later revealed to be a marketing stunt created by a Portuguese production company, and Teresa Fidlago does not exist in reality.\n\nThe Teresa Fidlago story is often cited as an example of how urban legends and hoaxes can spread rapidly through social media, often blurring the lines between fact and fiction.",
